ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This grouping of value sets contains concepts that represent delivery of a single live born newborn),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Diagnosis or Encounter Performed (diagnosis attribute). The intent of this data element is to identify a delivery of a single live born newborn.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with codes that identify the delivery of a single live born newborn. This is a grouping of ICD-10-CM and SNOMED CT codes.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
